{"tid":1959372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咩星座嘅人先最麻煩，煩撚到自己都憎","createTime":"2020-04-05T10:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T11:00:10.000Z","uid":268540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44abe006239615f45314a248c48d810ebaeb8c3c","tid":1959372,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"處女座<br />\n成日都好易睇穿一個人真心定假意，搞到唔想再信人，人地做少少嘢，自己已經ff到人地好多唔鐘意自己嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明睇穿曬人地嘅企圖，明知佢係呃鳩我自己都唔想踢爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明知個女仔玩鳩自己，明知佢當自己係兵，都唔敢遠離佢，驚佢覺得我好似嬲咗佢。明知人地講緊大話，仲要扮俾佢呃到，就係驚佢無面。<br />\n唉屌，做人好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地問有咩煩惱，又驚俾人覺得自己城府好深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時好憎自己成日諗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4c9be22086fd6d6b15f570742763ef80b15f69","tid":1959372,"uid":38098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"應該係信星座嘅人"},{"pid":"d0a8894b330055b9383c3c8dcd31326ed9510c02","tid":1959372,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b4c9be22086fd6d6b15f570742763ef80b15f69","tid":1959372,"uid":38098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"應該係信星座嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"有啲位都準嘅"},{"pid":"6c207edd5a5ea30e40ef24d9699ea8d4786c456c","tid":1959372,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"處女+1<br />\n少少野就會亂諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774ab5bc509b962bb122929786a56dd1985fc679","tid":1959372,"uid":268540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c207edd5a5ea30e40ef24d9699ea8d4786c456c","tid":1959372,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020